channel.title: Sythe SCAR Scripts
channel.description:
I realize that the "Complete User Posted Script List" was posted, this list contained every script on Moparisthebest.
Because of this I have decided to Post a "Complete User Posted Script List" From Sythe.org, All scripts came out of Scar>Tested Runescape Scripts, So almost all should be in great
working order!
I take no credit for these scripts in anyway, sharp, or form except for putting them all together.
They are Grouped in categorys as you can easily tell.
Please post feedback here as this took a bit to puttogether.
